This page explains how to build Xyst using make instead of ninja.

@section howto_make_build How to build Xyst with make instead of ninja

If ninja is not available, make is likely there. To clone and build using make
do

@code{.bash}
git clone https://codeberg.org/xyst/xyst.git && cd xyst
mkdir build && cd build
cmake ../src
make
@endcode

